>>>>>>> # Our position statement on the use of low or no calorie sweeteners
>>>>>>> Low or no calorie sweeteners receive much publicity and controversy
remains amongst both consumers and healthcare professionals surrounding their
use. This is in part explained by the inconsistent and sometimes contradictory
information that is presented in relation to their safety, role in weight
>>>>>>> We aim to review the current evidence and provide a set of
recommendations, as well as identify the gaps in research.
